Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.85,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}I wonder if I can see you, and beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.52,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}I just want to be stronger than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.44,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\blur5\fax-0.1}to hold you, all of, oh even the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.78,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}All the dreams end up as mere dreams, even if game's over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.86,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\blur5\fax-0.1}I won't give up my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.45,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}Even a hope may be said 'Just that's a thought'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:23.03,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax-0.1}so I still want to reach for you hoping you live your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.45,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}Only there's a truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:29.33,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}Living for making all the moments shine with proving all times
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.63,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,125)\blur5\fax-0.1}Just seeing your smiles, that's my dream
